    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You should use the <code>@JsonProperty</code> on the field you want to change the default name mapping.</p>\n\n<pre><code>class User{\n    @JsonProperty(\"first_name\")\n    protected String firstName;\n    protected String getFirstName(){return firstName;}\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For more info: the <a href=\"http://jackson.codehaus.org/1.1.2/javadoc/org/codehaus/jackson/annotate/JsonProperty.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">API</a></p>\n"
  }, {
